Title: Releasing My First Udemy Course

Description:
Introduction We recently at Respond.io happily received our first compliance certification under the framework ISO 27001. This certification verifies your organization with the world‚Äôs best-known standard for information security management systems (ISMS), ensuring that the said organization has put in place a system to manage risks related to the security of data owned or handled by them.
As the person in charge of infrastructure security and one of the contributors on a small team leading this initiative, I would like to share a few tips for developers and DevOps enthusiasts who are less familiar with organizational compliance from a technical point of view.
